        <title>PSI as expected</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[sir.louen]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>I was drawn to frontity and was amazed to see in their frontpage this:<br>
</p><div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/original/1X/a6437244ac74ac1664d22099516d1a24a50e98f7.png" data-download-href="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/a6437244ac74ac1664d22099516d1a24a50e98f7" title="image"><img src="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/1X/a6437244ac74ac1664d22099516d1a24a50e98f7_2_690x341.png" alt="image" data-base62-sha1="nIPLjX5pS7FaWocu3R46L7Hn3cH" width="690" height="341" srcset="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/1X/a6437244ac74ac1664d22099516d1a24a50e98f7_2_690x341.png, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/1X/a6437244ac74ac1664d22099516d1a24a50e98f7_2_1035x511.png 1.5x, https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/1X/a6437244ac74ac1664d22099516d1a24a50e98f7_2_1380x682.png 2x" data-small-upload="https://community.frontity.org/uploads/default/optimized/1X/a6437244ac74ac1664d22099516d1a24a50e98f7_2_10x10.png"></a></div><p></p>
<p>But as expected:<br>
<a href="https://developers.google.com/speed/pagespeed/insights/?hl=en&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Ftwentytwenty.frontity.org%2F" class="onebox" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">https://developers.google.com/speed/pagespeed/insights/?hl=en&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Ftwentytwenty.frontity.org%2F</a></p>
<p>Can’t even reach 90 PSI for such a simple site mostly because, this amount of JS cannot keep it up.</p>
<p>Without a consistent 90+ PSI I doubt this is adequate given the future expectations for 2021-2022:<br>
